<HEADLINE> Istanbul Stock Exchange Index Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ANKARA, December 28 (Xinhua) -- Turkey's Istanbul Stock
Exchange National-100 Index closed at 2,584.73 on Monday, down
23.10 points, or 0.85 percent, from Friday's finish.
</P>
<P>
The trading was heavy with the turnover reaching over 67
trillion Turkish Liras (209 million U.S. dollars).
</P>
<P>
The financial index dropped 4.88 points, or 0.12 percent, to
close at 3,227.29 points, the industrial index fell 23.35 points,
or 1.15 percent, to close at 1,898.51 points and the services
index went down 131.81 points, or 3.53 percent, to close at
3,618.59 points. 
</P>
