<HEADLINE> Ugandan Taxi Drivers Urged to Improve Skills </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
KAMPALA, December 28 (Xinhua) -- Ugandan taxi and other public
service vehicle drivers have been urged to acquire professional
training on the job to help reduce road accidents in the country.
</P>
<P>
