He also said that there is need for the youths to unite for
development. Such organizations will lay a foundation for their
discipline, he added.
</P>
<P>
Uganda is regarded as one of the few countries in the world
where it is easy to obtain driving licenses and where many taxi
drivers are found speeding on roads in poor conditions.
</P>
<P>
Overloading, reckless driving and speeding often result in
fatal accidents on feeder roads in the countryside. 
