<HEADLINE> CICB to Provide Credit Support for Oil Refining Group </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, December 29 (Xinhua) -- The China Industrial and
Commercial Bank (CICB) will provide a credit line of seven billion
yuan in working capital loans for the China Petro-Chemical
Industrial Group in 1999, according to an agreement signed today
by the two sides.
</P>
<P>
Under the agreement, the CICB will list the group and its
subsidiaries as the bank's basic clients for preferential
support. In addition, the CICB will further increase its loans to
