preferential banking services including bill acceptance, letters
of credit, credit cards, discounting, and foreign exchange credit
lines, as well as foreign exchange loans, settlements and
consultation.
</P>
<P>
The spokesman said that in August this year, the CICB selected
91 profitable large and medium-sized enterprises with good credit
as its key clients, for which the bank will provide high-quality
preferential banking services.  
