<HEADLINE> Senior Official Expelled from Party for Corruption (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
According to an investigative report from the CPC Central
Commission for Discipline Inspection, Meng was born to a poor
family and was a cowherd in his childhood. "It was the Party that
provided him with the chance to receive a college education," the
report said.
</P>
