<HEADLINE> Hong Kong Stocks Close Slightly Higher </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, December 29 (Xinhua) -- Hong Kong stocks gained
55.83 points, or 0.55 percent, to close at 10,225.97 Tuesday.
</P>
<P>
The turnover remained low and, boosted by futures trading, it
eventually reached 1.327 billion HK dollars (170 million
U.S. dollars), 105 million HK dollars (13 million U.S. dollars)
more than that of Monday.
</P>
<P>
