indignation"over the verdict of a Tokyo court in the Shiro Azuma
diary case.
</P>
<P>
"A handful of Japanese rightists are attempting to deny the
Nanjing Massacre by using judicial procedures," Zhu Bangzao said
yesterday in Beijing.  
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
</DOC>
